From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia

This is a category of all short articles associated with the Translation Task Force and part of the Emergency medicine chapter. This category is required for the functioning of this tool which lists all articles for translation that do not yet exist in a particular language. It is a hidden category which means that our readers do not see it.

It should not be merged with any other category, and articles should show up in both this and the main category to ensure the tool works optimally.


This is a maintenance category, used for maintenance of the Wikipedia project. It is not part of the encyclopedia and contains non-article pages, or groups articles by status rather than subject. Do not include this category in content categories (except for eponymous maintenance categories).
This is a hidden category. It is not shown on its member pages, unless the corresponding user preference (Appearance → Show hidden categories) is set.
